'''布薩庫山'''（{{lang-pt|Serra do Buçaco}}）是位於葡萄牙的一處[[山脈|山脈]]<ref>Frommer's Portugal Darwin Porter, Danforth Prince - 2012 p294 "BY CAR From Coimbra, head northeast along Route 110 to the town of Penacova at the foot of the Serra do Buçaco. From there, continue north, following signposts along a small secondary road.</ref><ref>Lonely Planet Portugal Regis St. Louis, Robert Landon - 2007 p316 Serra do Buçaco</ref>。布薩庫山的最高峰是克魯斯山，高549米。山脈內有一個創建於1628年的[[加爾默羅會|加爾默羅會]][[修道院|修道院]]。
